  . .  |  . .
  . x  |  . . ] :w bind!

[ x .  |  . .
  . .  |  x .
  . .  |  . . ] :x bind!

[ . .  |  . .
  x .  |  . .
  . .  |  x . ] :y bind!

[ x .  |  . .
  . .  |  . .
  . .  |  x . ] :z bind!

